prompt.prompt_text: Show the number of branches in each municipality.

results.sql: select    "_key_id_",    "_metric_value_",    count(*) over () as "total_rows_count" from (   with recursive      "_metric_value__1" as (       select          "obec_dwh_1"."kod_obec" as "_key_id_",          count("zsj_d_dwh_1"."kod_zsj_d") as "_metric_value__1",          count("zsj_d_dwh_1"."kod_zsj_d") as "_metric_value__2"       from "zsj_d_dwh_1"         join "cast_obec_dwh_1"         on "zsj_d_dwh_1"."kod_cast_obec" = "cast_obec_dwh_1"."kod_cast_obec"         join "obec_dwh_1"         on "cast_obec_dwh_1"."kod_obec" = "obec_dwh_1"."kod_obec"       where (         "obec_dwh_1"."y_max" > 46         and "obec_dwh_1"."y_min" < 54         and "obec_dwh_1"."x_max" > 1         and "obec_dwh_1"."x_min" < 28       )       group by 1       order by "_key_id_" asc     ),      "_metric_value__3" as (       select          "obec_dwh_1"."kod_obec" as "_key_id_",          count("all_branches_1"."id") as "_metric_value__3"       from "all_branches_1"         join "zsj_d_dwh_1"         on "all_branches_1"."kod_zsj_d" = "zsj_d_dwh_1"."kod_zsj_d"         join "cast_obec_dwh_1"         on "zsj_d_dwh_1"."kod_cast_obec" = "cast_obec_dwh_1"."kod_cast_obec"         join "obec_dwh_1"         on "cast_obec_dwh_1"."kod_obec" = "obec_dwh_1"."kod_obec"       where (         "obec_dwh_1"."y_max" > 46         and "obec_dwh_1"."y_min" < 54         and "obec_dwh_1"."x_max" > 1         and "obec_dwh_1"."x_min" < 28       )       group by 1       order by "_key_id_" asc     )   select      coalesce(       "_metric_value__1"."_key_id_",        "_metric_value__3"."_key_id_"     ) as "_key_id_",      round(coalesce(   round((("_metric_value__1" - "_metric_value__2") + coalesce(   "_metric_value__3",    cast(0.0 as numeric) ))::numeric, 0),    cast(0.0 as numeric) )::numeric, 0) as "_metric_value_"   from "_metric_value__1"     full outer join "_metric_value__3"     on "_metric_value__1"."_key_id_" = "_metric_value__3"."_key_id_"   group by      1,      "_metric_value__1",      "_metric_value__2",      "_metric_value__3"   order by      1 asc,      "_metric_value__1" asc,      "_metric_value__2" asc,      "_metric_value__3" asc    ) as "inner" limit 20000 offset 0
